Qiyaastii 0.8 ilaa 1.2 bilyan oo dad oo aduunka ah ayaa qaba cudurka gooryaanka oo dadka badanaaba ay aadka u saameysay ay ku noolyiin [[Lama-Dagaanka Hoose ee Afrika]], [[Latin America]], iyo Asia.<magaca tixraaca=Dold2011/><magaca tixraaca=Kei2010/><magaca tixraaca=Fen2012>{{cite journal|ugudambeyn=Fenwick|uguhoreyn=A|cinwaanka=cudurada kala duwan ee la dayacay ee culeyska dunida ah.|journal=Caafimaadka bulshada|taariiqda=Mar 2012|heerka=126|la sameeyay=3|boggag=233–6|pmid=22325616|doi=10.1016/j.puhe.2011.11.015}}</tixraaca> Tani waxay sameyneysaa gooryaan nooca ugu caansan ee [[gooryaanka carada laga qaado]].<tixraaca magaca=Kei2010>{{cite journal|ugu dambeeyo=Keiser|ugu horeeyo=J|qoraaga=Utzinger, J|cinwaanka=daawooyinka aan heyno iyo daawooyinka aan u baahannahaay ee loogaga hortaga cudurada goryaanka ugu muhiimsan.|journal=Hormarada ee daraasada gooryaanka |sannadka=2010|heerka=73|boggaga=197–230|pmid=20627144|doi=10.1016/s0065-308x(10)73008-6}}</tixraaca> ka bilaw 2010 waxay sababtay ku dhawaad 2,700 dhimasho ee kazoo bilaw hoos 3,400 ee 1990.<magaca tixraaca=Loz2012>{{cite journal|ugudambeyn=Lozano|uguhoreyn=R|title=Dhimashada aduunka iyom goboleedka ka bilaw 235 sababo oo dhimashada kooxda da’da 20 ee 1990 iyo 2010: falanqeyn nidaamsan oo daraasada Culeyska Cudurka Aduunka 2010.|journal=Lancet|taariiqda=Dec 15, 2012|heerka=380|la sameeyay=9859|boggag=2095–128|pmid=23245604|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(12)61728-0}}</tixraaca> Nooc kale oo''[[Gooryaanka]]'' wuxuu saameeyaa doofaarka.<tixraaca magaca=Dold2011/>

